OL,3,CMan who spied on children in Butlins
OL,4,Cchanging rooms is jailed
OL,6,FA man who spied on people and
OL,7,Fstockpiled indecent images of children
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for more than three
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FMark Simpson, formerly of Bellshill
OL,12,FClose, Hadrian Park in Wallsend,
OL,13,Frecorded footage and took photos of
OL,14,Fhis victims in the changing rooms at
OL,15,FButlins Skegness.
OL,17,FThe incidents took place between 2017-
OL,18,F2023. Thirty from Butlins, and four at
OL,19,Fa separate location.
