OL,3,CMan who spied on children in Butlins
OL,4,Cchanging rooms is jailed
OL,6,FOn 15 April 2023, a man reported his
OL,7,Fwife had been spied on. Officers
OL,8,Ftracked down Simpson and his phone was
OL,9,Fseized and handed over to the digital
OL,10,Fforensic unit for download.
OL,12,FThe device was assessed by a member of
OL,13,Fthe Paedophile Online Investigation
OL,14,FTeam who confirmed it contained
OL,15,Fmultiple videos of voyeurism.
