OL,3,CMan who spied on children in Butlins
OL,4,Cchanging rooms is jailed
OL,6,FThey also found videos containing
OL,7,Findecent images of children, and a
OL,8,Fhidden folder was also discovered
OL,9,Fwhich housed an app showing chat logs
OL,10,Fwhere he had exchanged indecent and
OL,11,Fprohibited images of children.
OL,13,FThe 51-year-old appeared at Newcastle
OL,14,FCrown Court for sentencing on Monday
OL,15,F20 October where he pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fmultiple charges including voyeurism
OL,17,Fand distributing indecent images.
OL,19,FHe was jailed for 38 months.
