OL,3,CMan who spied on children in Butlins
OL,4,Cchanging rooms is jailed
OL,6,FPolice Constable Andy Taylor, who led
OL,7,Fthe case, has praised everyone
OL,8,Finvolved in bringing Simpson to
OL,9,Fjustice.
OL,11,FHe said: "This case has undergone an
OL,12,Fextensive and detailed investigation,
OL,13,Finvolving the examination of multiple
OL,14,Fdevices and numerous hours of work.
OL,16,F"As a result, a comprehensive file was
OL,17,Fsubmitted to the Crown Prosecution
OL,18,FService (CPS), which led to the
OL,19,Fauthorization of 15 charges relating
OL,20,Fto possession of indecent images and
OL,21,Falso voyeurism against the suspect.
