OL,6,F"Given the strength of the evidence,
OL,7,Fthe suspect has pleaded guilty to all
OL,8,F15 offenses.
OL,10,F"This sentence aims to provide justice
OL,11,Ffor the victims whose privacy and
OL,12,Fpersonal space were violated.
OL,14,F"The case benefited from the support
OL,15,Fof various departments, and their
OL,16,Fcollaboration was instrumental in
OL,17,Fachieving this positive outcome.
OL,19,F"I would like to extend my gratitude
OL,20,Fto everyone involved in this process,
OL,21,Fto reach this positive outcome today."
